，站在历史正确一边，而不是相反。 来源：海外网"},"attached_info":"Cj4ImfSm14vh3NV0EAMaCDgxNTc1ODIxIM/PhZUGMAE4XkAfcgk1MzY4MjMwMjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb66b634bcf845c47acb0048dcf57742_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"32_1654795060.8747325","card_id":"Q_536717918","target":{"id":536717918,"title":"如何评价集度ROBODAY上发布的概念车ROBO-01？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/536717918","type":"question","created":1654689642,"answer_count":35,"follower_count":107,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[570,33053,780300],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"6月8日集度ROBODAY上发布了概念车ROBO-01，发布会有何亮点值得关注？ROBO-01将如何引领全新行业变革和产品升级？欢迎各位大佬前来建楼讨论。"},"attached_info":"Cj4ImfSm14vh3NV0EAMaCDgxNTUyNDEwIOqegpUGMAI4a0Agcgk1MzY3MTc5MTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-15126a386d6a22dea85642962c60e6e8_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"33_1654795060.8753228","card_id":"Q_536795340","target":{"id":536795340,"title":"6 月 8 日北京新增 1 例本土确诊病例，目前当地疫情情况如何？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/536795340","type":"question","created":1654732451,"answer_count":21,"follower_count":78,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[202,237,315,4080,566594],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"6月8日0时至24时，新增1例本土确诊病例（为6月7日诊断的无症状感染者转确诊病例），无新增疑似病例和无症状感染者；新增1例境外输入确诊病例，无新增疑似病例和无症状感染者。治愈出院26例。 境外输入确诊病例：中国台湾籍，6月7日从中国台湾到达北京首都机场，海关经健康筛查并进行核酸检测后，经闭环管理送至集中隔离酒店，当日报告核酸检测结果为阳性，6月8日诊断为确诊病例。 上述病例均已转至定点医院，已开展流行病学调查，按要求落实管控措施。北京昨日新增1例本土确诊病例"},"attached_info":"Cj4ImfSm14vh3NV0EAMaCDgxNTY